==English==

===Etymology===
From the old French ''grisel'', from the French ''gris'', [[grey]].

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɪzəl|-ɪzəl]]

===Noun===
'''grizzle'''
#(''colour'') a grey colour.
#:<table><tr><td>grizzle colour: &nbsp;</td><td bgcolor="#626461" width="80">&nbsp; </td></tr></table>
# grey [[hair]].
# a grey [[wig]].

===Adjective===
'''grizzle'''
#(''colour'') of a grey colour.

===Verb===
{{en-verb|grizzl|ing}}
# to make or become grey.

